homecoming is a 2009 american independent horror-thriller film , directed by morgan j. freeman and written by katie l. fetting , jake goldberger and frank hannah . the film follows a student couple , mike ( matt long ) and elizabeth ( jessica stroup ) , on their homecoming . elizabeth is taken home by mike 's ex-girlfriend shelby ( mischa barton ) after a road accident . shelby is soon revealed to be fixated on mike and subsequently treats elizabeth in a cruel and deranged manner .